com.enremmeta.rtb.dao

Interface DbService

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AerospikeDBService, CollectionsDbService, DynamoDBService, HazelcastService, RedisService

    public interface DbService
    Service providing one or more of the following:
    • DaoCounters
    • DaoMap
    • DaoShortLivedMap
    • DaoMapOfUserAttributes
    • DaoMapOfUserSegments
    If the service does not provide any of the above services, the appropriate getter for it MUST throw UnsupportedOperationException.
    Author:
    Gregory Golberg (grisha@alum.mit.edu)
